She takes a hit in the shoudler and is hit in the neck.  She falls 
and tumbles down the hill and rests next to Drillbit's body.  She 
stammers up and drags him inside the base. "HELP! HELP HIM!"  She ran 
back out and stood next to Terrorsaur with her small gun drawn. "You 
keep firing,and I shell help."  She said, straining to talk and meck 
fluid coming out of her neck wound and dripping on the ground.
